- Common submission mistakes and fixes
- Best practices for mathematical rigor

#### Step 6.3: Cross-Platform Integration
- Links to Agent A's predictions page
- Embed Agent C's audio demonstrations
- Integration with theory of everything page
- Unified navigation and branding

### **PHASE 7: Testing & Launch (Days 15-16)**

#### Step 7.1: Comprehensive Testing
- End-to-end workflow testing
- GPT review accuracy validation
- Lean verification stress testing
- UI/UX testing across devices
- Security and performance testing

#### Step 7.2: Beta Launch
- Limited beta with select users
- Feedback collection and iteration
- Bug fixes and optimizations
- Documentation completion

#### Step 7.3: Public Launch
- Full system deployment
- Marketing and announcement
- Academic community outreach
- Press release preparation

